                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d341">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00119 P.W./2–1645: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Personal Representative of President Roosevelt to Pope Pius XII</hi>
                        (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Taylor</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-02-21T13:00:00-04:00"
                            >February 21, 1945—1 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>23. Secret source within Government reports that you have had your “first talk”
                    with Ken Harada. We assume that if such a conversation had occurred you would of
                    course have so reported.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Grew</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
